column5: Hey all, moving this Friday to Buckhorn lake as the start of semi-sorta retirement begins. Attached a few picks of my new toy, and the house  - but who really cares about the house!
Hmmm, never been to Buckhorn. Hows the electrical on the house? Maybe you need an inspection?
Which part of Buckhorn did you land on? Upper - Lower?
How sweet it is! Walking out your backdoor to a lake front! Congrats on both!
Linvin' the dream for sure. I am a big Yammy fan so I love the boat, house and lake are nice too. Can't wait to get to that point myself...only about 20+ years
That is so awesome. Big Cliff is heading out, you are heading in, the cycle of life continues. Hope you enjoy it your spot looks phenomenal. Very jealous!
Which part of Buckhorn did you land on? Upper - Lower? We are on upper Buckhorn. Lots of water to fish!
Congrats f7. This may be the first place you can't wait to get home to, chores or not. Cut some lawn, make a cast, repeat.
